                <!-- Privacy Policy -->
                <div class="document-card" id="privacy-policy" data-category="privacy">
                    <div class="document-header">
                        <h3 class="document-title">PRIVACY POLICY</h3>
                        <div>
                            <span class="document-category">Privacy</span>
                            <span class="document-meta">Last updated: January 15, 2025</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="document-content">
                        <p>T.S.K.V. Spartacus is committed to protecting the privacy of our members. This policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information.</p>
                        
                        <h3>INFORMATION WE COLLECT</h3>
                        <p>We collect the following personal information when you become a member:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Full name</li>
                            <li>Student ID number</li>
                            <li>Email address</li>
                            <li>Phone number</li>
                            <li>Emergency contact information</li>
                            <li>Date of birth</li>
                            <li>Relevant health information (optional, for safety purposes)</li>
                            <li>Competition results and performance data (for participating members)</li>
                            <li>Payment information for membership fees and event registrations</li>
                        </ul>
                        
                        <h3>HOW WE USE YOUR INFORMATION</h3>
                        <p>Your personal information is used for:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Membership administration and communications</li>
                            <li>Organization of training sessions and competitions</li>
                            <li>Emergency contact in case of injury</li>
                            <li>Registration with relevant sports federations (with your consent)</li>
                            <li>Distribution of association newsletters and announcements</li>
                            <li>Processing payments for membership fees and events</li>
                            <li>Statistical analysis of membership demographics (anonymized)</li>
                        </ul>
                        
                        <h3>DATA STORAGE AND SECURITY</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Personal information is stored securely in digital form with appropriate access controls.</li>
                            <li>Access to member data is restricted to authorized Board members and necessary volunteers.</li>
                            <li>We retain your information only as long as necessary for the purposes listed above or as required by law.</li>
                            <li>We implement appropriate technical measures to protect your information.</li>
                        </ul>
                        
                        <h3>DATA SHARING</h3>
                        <p>We may share your information with:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Tilburg University Sports Center (for membership verification)</li>
                            <li>KNKF or other sports federations (for competition registration, with your consent)</li>
                            <li>Service providers who help us operate our association (e.g., email services)</li>
                            <li>Emergency medical personnel in case of injury</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>We will never sell your personal information to third parties.</p>
                        
                        <h3>YOUR RIGHTS</h3>
                        <p>Under the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), you have the right to:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Access your personal information</li>
                            <li>Correct inaccurate or incomplete information</li>
                            <li>Request deletion of your information (where applicable)</li>
                            <li>Object to certain processing of your information</li>
                            <li>Request a copy of your information in a portable format</li>
                            <li>Withdraw consent for optional data processing</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>To exercise these rights, please contact the Board at privacy@tskvspartacus.nl.</p>
                        
                        <h3>PHOTOS AND MEDIA</h3>
                        <p>During events and competitions, photographs and videos may be taken for promotional purposes, website content, and social media. If you do not wish to be photographed or recorded, please inform a Board member at the event or email media@tskvspartacus.nl.</p>
                        
                        <h3>CHANGES TO THIS POLICY</h3>
                        <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Significant changes will be communicated to members via email and on our website.</p>
                        
                        <h3>CONTACT</h3>
                        <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy or our data practices, please contact the Board at privacy@tskvspartacus.nl.</p>
                    </div>
